# More info: https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/#dockerignore-file
# Ignore everything by default and re-include only needed files
**

# Re-include Go source files (but not *_test.go)
!**/*.go
**/*_test.go

# Re-include Go module files
!go.mod
!go.sum
!.go-version

# Re-include embedded non-Go assets. The manager binary embeds the public
# network profiles via `//go:embed` in internal/cardano/publicnet/plan.go;
# without these in the build context, `docker build` fails with
# "pattern profiles/mainnet/*: no matching files found".
!internal/cardano/publicnet/profiles/**
